    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Twisted Reality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211520/extras/4094276b14931ed71931adf2849a6557.poster.avif?t=1760426007\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211520/extras/4094276b14931ed71931adf2849a6557.webm?t=1760426007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211520/extras/4094276b14931ed71931adf2849a6557.mp4?t=1760426007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your late-night train ride warps into a nightmare. Reality bends as you shift between horrifying dimensions. Each station becomes a terrifying puzzle box, challenging your sanity and survival skills. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use your phone</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211520/extras/13d27c4bf6f57474c839ea2d5508a150.poster.avif?t=1760426007\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211520/extras/13d27c4bf6f57474c839ea2d5508a150.webm?t=1760426007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211520/extras/13d27c4bf6f57474c839ea2d5508a150.mp4?t=1760426007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your smartphone is your only ally. Scan mysterious QR codes, follow AR pathways, and manipulate the warped environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
